The paper discusses a problem related to wireless networks, specifically LTE HetNets with carrier aggregation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also uses game theory to design a distributed algorithm, which suggests a possible connection to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). Additionally, the paper discusses power consumption, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also mentions comparing their scheme to different power strategies, which could relate to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
